{"tid":1247632,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"微博《古裝四美小花》投票選舉榜排名","createTime":"2019-06-21T07:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T09:01:47.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cefc6b2fbb3431223240a95bce0f807e11d168ed","tid":1247632,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"微博《古裝四美小花》投票選舉榜排名 <br />\n<br />\n第一名：鞠婧禕：58.3萬&mdash;&mdash;《新白娘子傳奇》白素貞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/dff5e4/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190616/20190616_198b40d26af6141d8248Uq7oXHHT9cOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fdff5e4%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190616%2F20190616_198b40d26af6141d8248Uq7oXHHT9cOz.jpg&h=81ea4c00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名：陳鈺琪：43.5萬&mdash;&mdash;《倚天屠龍記》趙敏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/01775c/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190616/20190616_eed7729e8730ea1890a7grhNxFSpRoN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F01775c%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190616%2F20190616_eed7729e8730ea1890a7grhNxFSpRoN3.jpg&h=e5e92e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三名：楊紫：39.1萬&mdash;&mdash;《香蜜沉沉燼如霜》錦覓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/20b216/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190616/20190616_f6d83f22f3471e81f521bdaguzBpyMON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F20b216%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190616%2F20190616_f6d83f22f3471e81f521bdaguzBpyMON.jpg&h=be6acd71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四位：劉詩詩：30.6萬&mdash;&mdash;《醉玲瓏》鳳卿塵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/3dac0c/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_190616/20190616_61e82ae2a3b2760ff6775iQ5TFGMEzBt.jpg\" 